Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:17.38,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}随性挑选着五彩的光线
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.59,0:23:19.62,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了协调我们的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.83,0:23:23.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}做自己想做的事情吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:50.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}阿珍诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么没精打采的  真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留了好多作业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  你连叹气都那么有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业  作业  作业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  大家合作一口气解决它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去千秋家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你们打算一起做作业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个一起  一会儿就能做完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们自己做也能很快完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是随便应付一下然后一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是用朦胧的睡眼来炫耀自己学习能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想啊  我们三个人都很优秀的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说的话你也应该是这边阵营的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.44,0:03:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装样子了  快上这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎加入白痴阵营
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给别人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起  我太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那修一是这边的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙  被她抢过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真同学  想参加直说就好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了真能参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴队伍也行？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打…扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:04:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到千秋会带男人回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚屋里去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说  以现有教育系统来看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做作业的才是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少义务教育期间如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向这家伙解释何为教育
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学  我醒悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快清醒过来  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打扰我们就滚到一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  我不打扰你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两个蠢货在  根本不可能认真学习
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不该带真来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  突然这么问我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是什么喜欢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人都在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知会来这么多客人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备些什么就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那现在做些简单的点心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我来帮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗  春香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也很有趣  春香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是帮大忙了  真同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了春香姐我什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真同学嘴挺甜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我替春香姐姐打多久的下手了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是做得最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  刚才居然叫「春香姐」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嬉皮笑脸  不是还有别的称呼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗  春香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留了好多作业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学  邀请我一起学习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（书法自习）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田同学  我有点事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算问了你也不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  真让人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野同学  我有点事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:06:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还是算了  我问本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学  能问你点事儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是我的错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才起你就一直无视我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样  现在确认了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许用这个名字称呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:08:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被千秋讨厌的原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇尺阁下  您以为呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇尺阁下是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砚台阁下  鄙人以为…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砚台阁下又是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.57,0:08:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是厌烦了毛笔阁下的愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛笔阁下？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛笔阁下是指我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  千秋开始试写了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许试写能反映出她此时的心境
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会出现被讨厌的原因的提示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:52.69,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（蠢货）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒是也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她点头了  得意之作？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从反面看也觉得很舒展
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是跟她道歉比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:23.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（对不起  真）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  零分！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有别在人家集中精神磨墨时搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别小瞧书法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才无视我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我呕心沥血之作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「蠢」写得很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是书法大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许再用这个名字叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野同学  内田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学她无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笤帚阁下  您以为呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是笤帚阁下的不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她得了失忆症
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明身为教师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却喜欢上二宫同学  所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  二宫小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人  您喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是回去比较…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈的  你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再让老子看见你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宫同学～！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  停电了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  正到关键时刻的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  向电视台申请重播
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向供电公司电话抗议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真同学因为千秋不让他来很伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真就是那个智障儿童吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实像是千秋讨厌的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买饮料回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  内田  下次带他来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让事情朝有趣的方向发展
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人放心不下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:06.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（24小时后）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你想来我家的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是因为想见春香姐这么邪恶的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  你不必自己说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果千秋不叫你来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不知道为何她就是不叫我来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为我的朋友就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变装一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被南同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋看到脸的话一定会认出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋的眼睛老是睁一半闭一半
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了不去看她不想看的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她大概没看过你的脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么首先换个可爱的发型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能换可爱的发型啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周身散发着野性气质啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好合适
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再穿上我的旧衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能穿女孩的衣服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天生一副花花公子风情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好合适
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香和千秋很快就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为使作战成功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望诸位全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理准备了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:46.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（30分钟后）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的学妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫作阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这名字太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（千秋的视角）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:27.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（内田  蠢货指数50%）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:27.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（夏奈  蠢货指数100%）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:34.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（阿珍  夏奈的朋友  蠢货指数信息不足）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:41.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（10分钟后）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  有位没见过的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我学妹阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想待到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话一起吃晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说春香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算都是女生也别在这儿脱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不像话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且像什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那全身都放松的脱法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍的脸色好像信号灯一样变了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么招式有这种效果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招…招式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我当没看到好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你这是什么反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像我在做什么下流的事情似的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了  我并不是喜欢才…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的不是这件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的是春香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起  我太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想扮作阿珍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了给春香她们设下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说得那么难听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是很纯粹很纯粹地想去南家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此只能变装成阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让夏奈借你衣服不就是了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来还有这招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.27,0:17:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总是穿夏奈的确实会让人起疑心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然衣服还是得买
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩买女装不是很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  内田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样买女装也不奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  幸好我家就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  去买吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  内田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这衣服以后也就借给我怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也必须戴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:51.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（天使牌胸罩畅销中）\N{\fs16}Angel Brassiere{\fsp43}　{\fsp1}{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…前几天来我们家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这个我还是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你选择适合的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始都会不好意思的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先得量下尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能脱掉衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能脱掉衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸膛是如此强健啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我量了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴…暴…暴露了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴…暴露了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要戴还是太早了些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定很快就会变大的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候再买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没暴露吧  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍的脸色又成信号灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:20:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚洗澡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  因为今天体育课上流了许多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  我还当这是鬓角呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到是耳毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  千秋  稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来咱家这位暂时也不用戴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  今天的晚饭吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了  千秋  耳毛得剪…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.21,0:23:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信  她居然是那蠢货的学妹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.15,0:23:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「三教九流」
